title: Leading telecommunication companies in Norway 2019 , by turnover
summary: This bar chart has 20 columns on the x axis representing Telecom Name, and Turnover in million NOK in each Telecom Name on the y axis.
The maximum Turnover in million NOK 124756.0 is found at Telecom Name Telenor ASA and the minimum is found at Netel AS where Telecom Name is 486.0.
The difference of Turnover in million NOK between the highest and lowest Telecom Name is 124270.0.

max_summary: This bar chart has 20 columns on the x axis representing Telecom Name, and Turnover in million NOK in each Telecom Name on the y axis.
The maximum Turnover in million NOK 124756.0 is found at Telecom Name Telenor ASA and the minimum is found at Netel AS where Telecom Name is 486.0.
Telecom Name Telenor Norge AS has the second highest value for Turnover in million NOK.
The Turnover in million NOK of Telecom Name Netel AS is 256.7% smaller than the maximum value at Telenor ASA.
Turnover in million NOK at Telecom Name Telenor ASA is 124756.0 , second place is Telenor Norge AS at 24669.0, and thirdly is Telia Norge AS at 9091.0.
The highest value 124756.0 at Telenor ASA is almost 13.7 times larger than the average value 9109.45.
The Turnover in million NOK is 182189.0 if we add up values of all Telecom Names.
